channel.title: CorruptedPkz
channel.description:
Features:
[b]PvP Features[/b] - Specials work 100% - The vengeance GFX is 100% animated. - Perfect PvP Wilderness levels - Rune Defender Emote - BarrelChest Anchor Emote - Dark bow spec - Amazing Combat System (No following) - Rune crossbow emote with dragon bolt special attack.
[b]Player vs Monster Features[/b] - 100% Dagganoth kings with real like effects - Metal Dragons - Green Dragon's - Many Place's to Train - 100% Perfect Combat - Slayer monsters - Kalphite Queen - King Black Dragon - Chaos Elemental
[b]- Minigame Features![/b] -Barrows is fully working Need spade to dig -Fight Caves -Pest Control 100% (Npc's, Need Certain Damage,Spinner's heal Npc's Attack. -Assault minigame (still Bieng Working on) -Duel Arena (100% Staking And Rules) -Warrior's Guild 30% (Animated Armor's for token's then Cyclop's For Defender's)
[b]Quest Features[/b] -Few Quest's Complete them for Reward's.
[b]Skilling and Other Features[/b] -All Skills work 100% (Construction, Farming & Hunter doesnt work properly tho) -Slayer updated with player-monster task precision. - Fast training (600xp/hit) - Money making can be Difficult. ( good economy ) - equipment screen - Skillcape emotes! - Banking works 100% - Great and stable economy - Working spell timers / spells! - Donations accepted! - Great staff!
-Awesome donator benefits!
